	Does not actually use ncurses, but detects it in order to
	determine terminfo details

	Includes various fixes for gnutls support. See:
	https://sourceforge.net/p/slrn/mailman/message/35246986

	Use long-int variant of abs(). See:
	https://sourceforge.net/p/slrn/mailman/message/35246987
<<
